                     <interp inst="t18370227-886-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>for stealing, on the <rs id="t18370227-cd-156" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370227-886-offence-1 t18370227-cd-156"></join>10th of February</rs>, 1 shirt, value 6<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370227-name-1264" type="victimName">
